                             fractal
                A simple fractal drawer using SDL

                     (c) Adrien Aucher 2011
              MIT license (see LICENSE for details)

fractal is a simple SDL application that displays a Mandelbrot set.

Commands:
---------
escape        quit
u             update display
r             reset display
arrows        move
+             max iterations per pixel + 10 (depth)
-             max iterations per pixel - 10 (depth)
CTRL+`+`      zoom+ x2
CTRL+`-`      zoom- x2
click + drag  zoom (box)
